      "bodyColor": "#7ab87a",
      "bodySize": 22,
      "bullets": [],
      "codeText": "1. Clone a trusted site with gophish or evilginx2\n2. Craft lure email — invoice, password reset, urgent HR notice\n3. Host payload (Office macro, ISO, LNK) or credential harvester\n4. Send via typosquatted domain with valid TLS cert\n5. Monitor for callbacks",
